<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>{{ title or "RBES White Paper" }}</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: "Georgia", "Times New Roman", serif;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #111;
      background: #fff;
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 3rem auto;
      padding: 0 1.25rem;
    }
    header {
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #000;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }
    h2 {
      font-size: 1.35rem;
      margin-top: 2.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
      padding-top: 1rem;
    }
    h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-top: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      font-weight: 600;
    }
    p {
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    ul, ol {
      margin-left: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }
    li { margin-bottom: 0.25rem; }
    table {
      border-collapse: collapse;
      width: 100%;
      margin: 1.5rem 0;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    th, td {
      border: 1px solid #999;
      padding: 0.4rem 0.6rem;
      text-align: left;
      vertical-align: top;
    }
    blockquote {
      margin: 1.5rem 1rem;
      padding-left: 1rem;
      border-left: 3px solid #333;
      font-style: italic;
    }
    code {
      background: #f6f6f6;
      padding: 0.1rem 0.25rem;
      font-family: "Menlo", monospace;
      font-size: 0.95em;
    }
    footer {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #000;
      padding-top: 1rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      text-align: center;
    }
    footer a { color: inherit; text-decoration: underline; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>{{ title }}</h1>
    <p><strong>Ben Shepard &amp; Job Zheng</strong><br>Bangkok · November 2025</p>
    <p><em>Rulebreakers English Studios White Paper Series · Draft v0.3</em></p>
  </header>

  <main>
    {{ content | safe }}
  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>© 2025 Rulebreakers English Studios · This document is an evolving public draft.<br>
    <a href="/">← Return to RBES Plan</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
